entries.femaleVariant: This arm... it is not mine! None of this me! Cold, dead metal! All of it!
Help! Someone please help me! Anyone!
What happened?
What happened? Your implants, they look... half-done.
Done or not done... it is of no importance!
A bhikku does not defile his body through cybermodification. It is against... the pratimoksha!
Where's your brother now?
Why'd they do it?
Makes no sense. Who'd go and do something like this? And why?
Maelstrom...
How 'bout your brother? He still with 'em?
Yes. I was first. Then they were trying to decide how... how to modfiy him.
I'm here to help.
What's in it for me?
What's in it for me? I don't work for free, y'know.
I cannot offer anything more than my gratitude. Just this once, please, make an exception.
The universe shall compensate you.
I'd rather not get involved.
Sorry, but I'm not lookin' to get involved with Maelstrom.
I understand. It is a lot to ask of one. My brother never hurt anyone. Someone shall save him.
All right, I'll help.
Gotta admit, you really know how to tug at those heartstrings. I'll help your brother.
Fine, I'll help. But just so you know, things might get ugly. Maelstrom doesn't mess around...
I do not know how to thank you. They are keeping him in a shop just north of here.
You shall find it next to the road along the docks.
We were out begging for alms when... when they approached us.
They laughed at us and asked if we would take implants as a donation.
They looked... more machine than human. They told us they would improve us, like tools.
You look like someone who can reason with these people. I beg you, please, help my brother!
I only hope it is not too late. I do not wish for him to end up like... like I have.
Please! Someone, help me!
Wh-what have I done to deserve this? To fall victim to Hinsa?!
It itches... should it itch? Why do I feel anything? It... it is nothing but unfeeling metal!
Calm down... Phew... Forget your own soul. You must save his.
Are you, uh... are you OK?
A monk with implants?
Hold on... somebody forced you?
Don't you take a vow against chippin' implants?
entries.maleVariant: Don't you, uh, take a vow against chippin' implants?

entries.femaleVariant: Of course we do! You think I did this to myself?!
I apologize I cannot bow in greeting. I am still... adjusting to my situation.
Not just me – my brother, too. They drugged us... desecrated my body.
Anyone?!
And all the while, they mocked me... How can you do this to a fellow human being and still mock them?
And yet... they knew about this! For me there is no return...
Gonna kill those assholes.
Chromesucking psychos... It won't be easy. Maelstrom never goes down the easy route...
The fucking clowns...
How poetic - a monk in distress... They should include this in your epic.
What're you gonna do – cross your legs and meditate till they drop dead?
Wish you'd drop dead...
There must be some other way. Help us, please, but without any bloodshed – I beg you.
I'll see what I can do... Either way, your brother's getting out.
entries.maleVariant: I'll see what I can do... Either way, your brother's gettin' out.

entries.femaleVariant: Help us, please... but without any bloodshed – I beg you.
[Show middle finger]
